description: Best practices for using Prisma ORM
globs: "**/*.{js,ts}"

- Use proper migration strategy
- Implement proper seeding approach
- Use proper transaction management
- Implement proper connection pooling
- Use proper database indexing strategy
- Implement proper query optimization
- Use proper pagination
- Implement proper soft delete pattern when applicable
- Use proper audit logging
- Implement proper schema validation
- Use proper relations (associations)
- Implement proper cascade behaviors
- Use proper database normalization 